    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other one was from 2:00 or 3:00 to 11:00 or 12:00, and then was the night shift.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, either of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I rotated, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember there was in air raids, which was eerie because I was not allowed to go to a public-- what do you call it-- bunker.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to run wherever I wanted to go and I was stopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to go to a basement and I said, I will ride home, I'll ride home with my little star.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just, you know, kind of hid it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
